      <description translate="no">
        <p>- Parabolic has been rewritten in C# from C++</p>
        <p>- Added support for playlist quality options</p>
        <p>- Added support for playlist subtitle options</p>
        <p>- Added support for reversing the download order of a playlist</p>
        <p>- Added support for remembering the previous Download Immediately selection in the add download dialog</p>
        <p>- Improved the design and usability of the Windows version of Parabolic</p>
        <p>- Fixed an issue where Parabolic crashed when adding large amounts of downloads from a playlist</p>
        <p>- Fixed an issue where Parabolic crashed when validating certain URLs</p>
        <p>- Fixed an issue where Parabolic refused to start</p>
        <p>- Updated yt-dlp</p>
